<H3> <TI>   Price Rises in 1994 Forecast </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Price Rises in 1994 Forecast </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CE0370B Beijing ZHONGHUA DISAN CHANYE BAO in Chinese 14 
Feb 94 p 2 </F>

<F P=103> 94CE0370B </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGHUA DISAN CHANYE BAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


