<H3> <TI>   New Tax System Now Under `Normal Operation' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Tax System Now Under `Normal Operation' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CE0389B Beijing JINGJI RIBAO in Chinese 1 Mar 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 94CE0389B </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing JINGJI RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


