<F P=106> [Article by Chen Zhenhong [7115 6297 7703]: ``MEI's </F>
Institute 23 Develops Reeling Fiber Optic Cable, Reeling 
Apparatus''] 
  [Summary] The reeling optical cable and reeling apparatus 
developed by MEI's Institute 23 has been formally certified. 
This cable, containing four to six fibers, has an external 
diameter of 4 mm and comes with a burn-resistant jacket. The 
reeling apparatus, consisting of a tractor and a reeling 
machine, can be manually operated or remote-controlled (for high 
overhead cable laying). 

