electric 
buses, freight EVs, 3-wheeled EVs, 2-wheeled EVs, etc. China 
already has the capability of small batch production of electric 
bicycles, 3-wheeled EVs, and electric wheelchairs, with electric 
automobiles remaining in the laboratory-prototype stage. 
