<TEXT>
Set   for Zhengzhou 

<F P=102> 94P60155B Beijing KEJI RIBAO [SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY DAILY] 
in Chinese 12 Feb 94 p 3 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60155B </F>
