<TEXT>
Wuhan 

<F P=102>   94P60155C Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
NEWS] in Chinese 25 Feb 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60155C </F>
